Package com.ibm.streams.management.domain

Interface LoggingPropertiesMXBean

public interface LoggingPropertiesMXBean
LoggingPropertiesMXBean provides attributes, operations, and notifications for working with Streams logging properties.

ObjectNameBuilder.domainPropertyGroup(String, com.ibm.streams.management.domain.DomainMXBean.PropertyGroup) can be used with a groupName of LOG to build the ObjectName for a LoggingPropertiesMXBean.

Notifications:
A LoggingPropertiesMXBean supports sending the following notifications:

javax.management.AttributeChangeNotification.ATTRIBUTE_CHANGE
Only a subset of the attributes support attribute change notification. A note is included in the attribute description for each attribute that supports attribute change notification
